urs d&#233;lais.<br><br>Avant de vous rendre en gare, nous vous recommandons de v&#233;rifier les horaires de vos trains.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","disruption_id":"4962e4f8-27a5-4026-94f6-1a07533b58b0"},{"id":"14f54698-5490-4afc-8cc7-cb13ab69684e","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260505T030000","end":"20260506T030000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260418T134142","cause":"TRAVAUX","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Ligne R : Paris Lyon <> Montargis \/ Montereau 04\/05-29\/05","message":"<p>P&#233;riode : en semaine d&#232;s 23h15<br><br>Dates : du lundi 04 mai au vendredi 29 mai, sauf les week-end et jours f&#233;ri&#233;s.<br><br>Le trafic est interrompu entre Paris Gare de Lyon et Montargis et entre Paris Gare de Lyon et Montereau.<br><br>Un service de bus de remplacement est mis en place, avec desserte des gares interm&#233;diaires.<br><br>Les horaires du calculateur d'itin&#233;raire tiennent compte des travaux.<\/p><p>Motif : travaux de maintenance sur le r&#233;seau ferroviaire.&nbsp;<\/p>","shortMessage":"Arrêt(s) non desservi(s)","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61414","name":"Montereau (Montereau-Fault-Yonne)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:411483","name":"Montargis (Montargis)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61414","name":"Montereau (Montereau-Fault-Yonne)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:411483","name":"Montargis (Montargis)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"}}],"disruption_id":"75ddf55a-2706-463d-b733-bc6c9b9811c4"},{"id":"a47aa17d-655e-4ec4-b594-7b897f106